<h2><%= config.topic %></h2>

<div>
분량: <%= config.minChars %>자 이상  
현재 글자수 : <span id="count">0</span>  
(공백 미포함: <span id="count2">0</span>)
</div>

<form method="POST" action="/submit" onsubmit="return confirmSubmit()">

<textarea id="editor" name="content" rows="15"><%= submission ? submission.content : "" %></textarea>

<button type="submit">제출</button>

</form>

<script src="/editor.js"></script>